 overflow: hidden; text-overflow: ellipsis; white-space: nowrap;\">保质天数：36个月</li>\r\n</ul>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><img style=\"border: 0px; vertical-align: middle; margin-top: 0px;\" src=\"/images/upload/fckautosave/201409/1411968564-1.gif\" alt=\"\" /></p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【产品特点】：全新神奇吸水层：更多吸收，依然超薄！升级后的吸水层能比以前吸收更多尿湿，却始终保持超薄舒适，宝宝晚上动得更自在，睡得更舒服，白天玩得更开心！档位合身剪裁：吸收更多，但档位体积比以往产品明显减少，不再像以前臃肿累赘棉柔透气外层：升级产品更柔软，更透气，更加呵护宝宝皮肤，使宝宝皮肤干爽健康 芦荟亲肤层：含有芦荟等亲肤精华，能在小屁股上形成保护层，帮助避免尿便刺激。</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; font-size: 12px; line-height: 30px; color: rgb(153, 153, 153); font-family: \'Microsoft YaHei\', \'Hiragino Sans GB\', Verdana, sans-serif; font-style: normal; font-variant: normal; font-weight: normal; letter-spacing: normal; orphans: auto; text-align: left; text-indent: 0px; text-transform: none; white-space: normal; widows: auto; word-spacing: 0px; -webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">【适用范围】：0-5公斤宝宝</p>\r\n<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; border: 0px; fon